OL,3,CFormer Jersey Catholic priest charged
OL,4,Cwith 10 child sex offences
OL,6,FA former Jersey Catholic priest has
OL,7,Fbeen charged with 10 sexual crimes
OL,8,Fagainst a child on the island.
OL,10,FPiotr Antoni Glas, 60, is alleged to
OL,11,Fhave committed the offences between
OL,12,F2004 and 2007.
OL,14,FHe no longer resides or serves in
OL,15,FJersey but appeared at the
OL,16,FMagistrates' Court in St Helier on
OL,17,FMonday 24 June.
