OL,3,CFormer Jersey Catholic priest charged
OL,4,Cwith 10 child sex offences
OL,6,FMr Glas spoke only to confirm his name
OL,7,Fand address - he lives in Southampton
OL,8,Fand has connections in both the UK and
OL,9,Fthe Isle of Wight.
OL,11,FITV News understands congregations
OL,12,Facross the island and in the south of
OL,13,FEngland were told about the
OL,14,Fallegations during last Sunday's main
OL,15,Fmass.
OL,17,FMr Glas faces eight counts of gross
OL,18,Findecency with a child and two counts
OL,19,Fof indecent assault on a child.
