OL,4,Cwith 10 child sex offences
OL,6,FThe case was deemed "too serious" for
OL,7,Fthe Magistrates' Court and has been
OL,8,Freferred to the Royal Court to be
OL,9,Fheard on Friday 6 September.
OL,11,FMr Glas has been remanded on bail and
OL,12,Fwill remain in Jersey.
